name: Karesansui Project
tagline: Karesansui is an open-source virtualization management application made in Japan.
body:
### Dear users of Karesansui

The source code is still available, but this project is no longer in active development.
We are currently seeking new maintainers and any feedback would be appreciated.
Please see [here](https://github.com/karesansui/karesansui/issues/26) if you are interested in becoming a project maintainer.

### About Karesansui

Karesansui is an open-source virtualization management application made in Japan.
It's smart graphical user interface lowers your management cost, and brings a total management/audit solution for both physical and virtual servers. Full featured RESTful interface allows customizing and integration with other management/billing systems.
